overview: High5store is an online mall with an array of designs from a number of skilled designers across the country. As an intermediary for buyers and sellers, it houses apparels for women like dress materials, tunics, skirts, dresses, sarees, duppatas, kurtis, accessories like bags, stoles and jewelry; Home décor like wall hangings, wall stickers, box, vase , Home furnishing like cushion covers, table runners and mats , eatables like chocolates and so on. All the products in this online store are one of a kind, rich and are freshly detailed in nature. By serving to be a binding platform for buyers and sellers, it renders cost effectiveness to both buyers and sellers. High5store.com is a highly user-friendly website along with comprehensive details about every procedure and products that it accommodates. It also guarantees on time delivery and other services that paves way for a gratifying experience.
